00:38:42.400 --> 00:38:43.240
Hello.

00:38:54.520 --> 00:38:55.920
There's one breathing here.

00:38:57.280 --> 00:38:58.160
Are you done?

00:39:25.640 --> 00:39:28.880
Doctor, how much longer can I live?

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.480
We will try our best.

00:39:34.840 --> 00:39:37.560
I have a sister named Tong Lingdang.

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:40.280
She works in the command center of the Brigade.

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:43.080
If she asks me,

00:39:43.880 --> 00:39:45.560
don't tell her I died here.

00:39:46.520 --> 00:39:47.440
Just say

00:39:48.960 --> 00:39:50.640
I fought with the Japanese.

00:39:54.600 --> 00:39:55.480
Thank you.

00:40:13.320 --> 00:40:15.480
You Chinese like to waste your time

00:40:15.640 --> 00:40:17.720
waste your time on these useless things.

00:40:19.600 --> 00:40:21.600
Don't say that, Mr. Tanaka.

00:40:22.400 --> 00:40:24.240
In terms of cultivation, you can work hard.

00:40:24.560 --> 00:40:25.640
and don't care about others.

00:40:26.200 --> 00:40:27.320
In terms of governing the world,

00:40:27.840 --> 00:40:29.160
some toys

00:40:29.360 --> 00:40:31.000
can be entertained.

00:40:33.520 --> 00:40:35.040
In your eyes,

00:40:35.440 --> 00:40:37.760
is a fighter who doesn't fear power.

00:40:37.920 --> 00:40:38.880
In my opinion,

00:40:39.080 --> 00:40:41.640
is just another powerful weapon.

00:40:41.680 --> 00:40:43.960
power and power are different.

00:40:44.360 --> 00:40:45.240
Shut up!

00:40:45.600 --> 00:40:48.040
Don't interrupt when adults are talking.

00:40:50.440 --> 00:40:52.040
All right, stop talking.

00:40:52.480 --> 00:40:54.240
I have something to do outside the city.

00:40:54.440 --> 00:40:55.520
Okay, I'll give you a ride.

00:40:55.800 --> 00:40:56.600
No need.

00:40:56.920 --> 00:40:58.800
I’ve been here for so long.

00:40:59.040 --> 00:41:00.720
I won’t bother you.

00:41:00.920 --> 00:41:01.960
Mr. Tian Yuan,

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:04.920
Thank you.

00:41:05.880 --> 00:41:06.880
Your son will do it for me.

00:41:07.080 --> 00:41:08.320
Just send me out of the city.

00:41:09.800 --> 00:41:10.880
What did you say?

00:41:11.200 --> 00:41:12.360
Your son is smart.

00:41:12.680 --> 00:41:14.480
I'll take him out to see the world.

00:41:14.720 --> 00:41:15.600
Don't worry.

00:41:15.760 --> 00:41:17.280
I'll be back in Shanzhou.

00:41:17.440 --> 00:41:17.960
By then,

00:41:18.160 --> 00:41:20.400
I will bring him back

00:41:20.560 --> 00:41:21.600
back to you.

00:41:23.440 --> 00:41:24.520
You...

00:41:29.400 --> 00:41:30.680
Is Luoyang fun?

00:41:31.120 --> 00:41:32.000
Of course.

00:41:32.240 --> 00:41:33.920
Okay, I'll go with you.

00:41:34.200 --> 00:41:35.040
Son.

00:41:35.240 --> 00:41:36.880
Father, don't worry.

00:41:47.400 --> 00:41:49.480
If anything happens to my son,

00:41:51.080 --> 00:41:53.200
I'll kill you.

00:42:24.080 --> 00:42:26.520
Why do you Communist Party accept everyone?

00:42:28.720 --> 00:42:29.680
What's wrong with him?

00:42:34.200 --> 00:42:35.000
Yes.

00:42:35.440 --> 00:42:36.240
Nothing.

00:42:36.560 --> 00:42:39.400
Could you please tell your leader

00:42:41.400 --> 00:42:42.320
another person?

00:42:43.520 --> 00:42:44.840
It's not that simple.

00:42:45.000 --> 00:42:45.920
It's not that easy.

00:42:46.200 --> 00:42:47.760
Can you be reasonable?

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:50.640
Okay.

00:42:51.200 --> 00:42:52.840
Promise me one thing first.

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:54.280
I'm going to Luoyang with you.

00:42:54.440 --> 00:42:55.160
No.

00:42:55.680 --> 00:42:56.640
It's too dangerous.

00:42:56.800 --> 00:42:57.520
It's dangerous.

00:42:57.720 --> 00:42:58.840
I can't let you go alone.

